divs: sighting detailsmy friend and i were sitting by the pool outside in the evening when we were in high school. i don't remember the exact day\time\year. it seemed like all of a sudden a craft appeared in our sight just above the trees about 150 feet away and decended behind the trees out of our sight. it had blinking lights around the midsection. didn't hear any sound but could make out the shape. it was right around dusk, we could see it clearly although couldn't make out small details. this was in south county, st. louis, mo around 1992.
trends: There have been 74 other sightings in St Louis
There were no other sightings in St Louis on or around June 30th 1992
Summary: Typical saucer shaped craft with dome appeared just above the trees
